Title

    My Weather App - A React Native App for Weather Information

Description

    A user-friendly React Native application that provides real-time and forecast weather information for various locations.

Features

    Displays current weather conditions (temperature, humidity, wind speed, etc.)
    Allows users to search for weather in different locations

Technologies Used:

    React Native (v0.74.1)
    Expo SDK
    react-native-vector-icons
    react-native-dotenv

Installation

    Prerequisites:
        Node.js and npm (or yarn) installed on your system.
        An Expo account (if using Expo)

    Cloning the Repository:
    Bash

    git clone https://github.com/your-username/weather-app.git

Running the App
npm start

Environment Variables

    The app uses environment variables for sensitive information like API keys.

Author

    Kingsley Ibe
